<doc f='redis/src/cluster.c' l='1364'>/* Update the node address to the IP address that can be extracted
 * from link-&gt;fd, and at the specified port.
 * Also disconnect the node link so that we&apos;ll connect again to the new
 * address.
 *
 * If the ip/port pair are already correct no operation is performed at
 * all.
 *
 * The function returns 0 if the node address is still the same,
 * otherwise 1 is returned. */</doc>
